      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.southgatefl.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The neighborhood’s historic centerpiece is a Victor Lundy‑designed community center and swimming pool on a five‑acre property by Phillippi Creek.",
