        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Southgate%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The area’s homes are mostly one‑story and feature retro styling, a hallmark of the early 1960s development.",
